    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>egg[s]</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 8-9 min for boiled egg[s]</p><p>Once done, drain and refill the pot with <strong>ice-cold water</strong> and the <strong>cooked egg[s]</strong>, then set aside to cool</p><p>Tip: Use the Gousto ice packs to chill the water!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1723204461455-x200.jpg",
