      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>chicken thighs</strong> and your <strong>curry powder </strong>in a large bowl with your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the <strong>coconut marinade </strong>(reserve the bowl!) and give it a good mix up</p><p>Add 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[6 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp]</span><strong> flour </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and, using your hands, scrunch the flour onto the chicken until fully coated – this is your <strong>coated chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1723204465993-x200.jpg",
